Title: Quantifying uncertainty for spikes estimated from calcium imaging data
Description: Implements selective inference procedures for spikes estimated via the L0 penalty, as described in Chen, Jewell, and Witten (2021+) <https://arxiv.org/abs/2103.07818>
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
